\n\r\nEven Better, <strong><em>Bra</em><em>in Stages: How to Raise Smart, Confident Kids and Have Fun Doing It, K – 5</em></strong>, our grade-by-grade guide through the elementary school years, will be available November 13, 2018 to make your life with kids a lot easier and way more pleasant!\r\n\r\n<strong>Please consider joining our community of people who want to make the world a better place for kids and parents by clicking the box at the bottom of this page to get exclusive tips.</strong>\r\n\r\nTo learn the surprising way Brain Stages came to be, click <a href=\"/blog/too-much-coincidence-not-to-be-part-of-the-cosmic-plan\">here.</a>\r\nTo find out more about the <em>Brain Stages</em> book, click <a href=\"/book.html\">here.</a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #1f1f1f;\">Thanks for visiting!</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #1f1f1f;\">                                                                                          Trish Wilkinson</span>\r\n\r\n</div>', 'About Brain Stages', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '22-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-10-04 23:24:22', '2018-10-04 23:24:22', '', 22, 'http://localhost:8888/2018/10/04/22-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
