;\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"/blog/the-best-pencil-grip-the-secret-to-easier-writing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">The Best Pencil Grip: The Secret to Easier Writing</span></a></h2>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"wsite-multicol-col\" style=\"width: 33.333333333333%; padding: 0 15px;\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"wsite-image wsite-image-border-none \" style=\"padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; text-align: right;\"><a href=\"/blog/names-for-ten-the-game-that-boosts-kids-math-skills\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\r\n<img style=\"width: auto; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/namesfor10-screenshot1-homepage_orig.jpg\" alt=\"Brain Stages Math Game\" />\r\n</a>\r\n<div style=\"display: block; font-size: 90%;\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"/blog/names-for-ten-the-game-that-boosts-kids-math-skills\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">“Names for 10” Game to Boost Math Skills</span></a></h2>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wsite-spacer\" style=\"height: 50px;\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '21-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-10-04 23:25:35', '2018-10-04 23:25:35', '', 21, 'http://localhost:8888/2018/10/04/21-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(43, 1, '2018-10-04 23:25:59', '2018-10-04 23:25:59', '&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"wsite-section-wrap\">\r\n<div class=\"wsite-section wsite-body-section wsite-background-10\">\r\n<div class=\"wsite-section-content\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"wsite-section-elements\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"wsite-multicol\">\r\n<div class=\"wsite-multicol-table-wrap\" style=\"margin: 0 -15px;\">\r\n<table class=\"wsite-multicol-table\">\r\n<tbody class=\"wsite-multicol-tbody\">\r\n<tr class=\"wsite-multicol-tr\">\r\n<td class=\"wsite-multicol-col\" style=\"width: 38.434782608696%; padding: 0 15px;\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"wsite-image wsite-image-border-none \" style=\"padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; text-align: left;\"><a>\r\n<img style=\"width: 396; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/brainstagescover-exp4-7d-stroke_1_orig.jpg\" alt=\"Picture\" />\r\n</a>\r\n<div style=\"display: block; font-size: 90%;\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.sandrajonaspublishing.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Sandra Jonas Publishing</a>\r\n<span style=\"color: #151515;\">Available November 13, 2018</span></div></td>\r\n<td class=\"wsite-multicol-col\" style=\"width: 61.565217391304%; padding: 0 15px;\">\r\n<h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\"><em><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Brain Stages</span></em>\r\n<span style=\"color: #515151; font-size: medium;\"><em><strong>How to Raise Smart, Confident Kids and Have Fun Doing It, K–5</strong></em></span></h2>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"height: 0px; overflow: hidden; width: 100%;\"></div>\r\n\r\n<hr class=\"styled-hr\" style=\"width: 100%;\" />\r\n\r\n<div style=\"height: 20px; overflow: hidden; width: 100%;\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left;\">Who says kids don’t come with instructions?\r\n\r\nWe’re pleased to announce the first edition of <em>Brain Stages</em>, a comprehensive grade-by-grade guide through the elementary school years.\r\n\r\n​Written in a friendly, conversational style, this book gives you useful tools to boost your kids’ brainpower and help them develop social skills, laying the foundation for them to become happy, successful adults.\r\n\r\nBacked by research and experience and filled with fun games, insider information, and amazing life hacks for raising kids, <em>Brain Stages</em> invites parents and caregivers to enjoy kids more and stress less while bringing up well-adjusted humans.\r\n\r\n“Finally, a guide to help your child enjoy learning based upon the latest brain research and explained by a veteran teacher, who offers parents fun, practical strategies.”\r\n— <strong>S. Craddu</strong><strong>ck, Licensed Educational Psychologist</strong>​</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'The Brain Stages Book', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '20-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-10-04 23:25:59', '2018-10-04 23:25:59', '', 20, 'http://localhost:8888/2018/10/04/20-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(44, 1, '2018-10-04 23:26:14', '2018-10-04 23:26:14', '&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"wsite-section-wrap\">\r\n<div class=\"wsite-section wsite-body-section wsite-background-3\">\r\n<div class=\"wsite-section-content\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"wsite-section-elements\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"wsite-multicol\">\r\n<div class=\"wsite-multicol-table-wrap\" style=\"margin: 0 -25px;\">\r\n<table class=\"wsite-multicol-table\">\r\n<tbody class=\"wsite-multicol-tbody\">\r\n<tr class=\"wsite-multicol-tr\">\r\n<td class=\"wsite-multicol-col\" style=\"width: 54.941860465116%; padding: 0 25px;\">\r\n<h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\"><span style=\"color: #248d6c;\">Learn More About Brain Stages</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"display: table; width: auto; position: relative; float: left; max-width: 100%; ;clear: left; margin-top: 4px; *margin-top: 8px;\"><a><img class=\"galleryImageBorder wsite-image\" style=\"border-width: 0; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px 20px 10px 0px;\" src=\"http://thebrainstages.com/uploads/1/1/4/0/114011163/published/twilkinson-tealblouse.jpg?1518317464\" alt=\"Picture\" /></a></span>\r\n<div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"display: block;\">Hi there,\r\n\r\nDo you have a question? Would you like to submit a video with your child that you think would be helpful for other parents and their kids? Would you like me to speak or do a workshop in your community?\r\n\r\nWhatever is on your mind, I\'d love to hear from you! I\'ll respond within 24 hours.\r\n\r\nTrish Wilkinson\r\nCo-author\r\n<em>Brain Stages — </em><em>How to Raise Smart, Confident Kids and Have Fun Doing It,\r\nK – 5</em>\r\nAvailable August 28, 2018, <a href=\"https://www.sandrajonaspublishing.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Sandra Jonas Publishing</a>\r\n​</div>\r\n\r\n<hr style=\"width: 100%; clear: both; visibility: hidden;\" />\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wsite-spacer\" style=\"height: 50px;\"></div></td>\r\n<td class=\"wsite-multicol-col\" style=\"width: 45.058139534884%; padding: 